metadata.name: OMI Inner Circle #1
metadata.description:
Celebrating the OMI Inner Circle community with this First Edition Emblem.

The OMI Inner Circle was created by Jake & Rico. Its purpose is to bring the Veve & OMI Community together as one. 

The movement began with Jake & Rico, creating hundreds of Inner Circle PFP's for users all over Twitter. Everyone soon noticed the viral red ring PFP and wanted to be involved! 

This is the first Exclusive Inner Circle NFT Emblem. Limited to 250 pieces.

Join the OMI Inner Circle - Add the Red Ring to your Twitter PFP!  
www.omicircle.xyz
